      "content": "surrender... i never thought about it like that. i always thought giving up was just being weak or something. but when you say it like that... it almost sounds like a relief. like, if i just stopped trying to force this life to work, maybe the weight would finally go away. it's like the only way to actually find peace is to just stop existing in this version of reality.",
